Introduction

Wow is a South Korean rapper under Beat Interactive. He is the main rapper of the boy group A.C.E.

In 2017, he, and his fellow members Kim Byeongkwan and Donghun, became a contestant on the JTBC's new survival show MIXNINE. He was eliminated in the episode 13 after achieving 11th place.
